description: Provided comprehensive nursing care to elderly patients in a 200-bed hospital. Managed medication administration, patient assessments, and collaborated with multidisciplinary teams. Specialized in geriatric care and dementia support.

Worked in the general medical ward providing care to patients with various medical conditions. Assisted with patient admissions, discharges, and care planning. Participated in quality improvement initiatives.
Currently working as an agency nurse providing flexible healthcare services across various healthcare facilities in London. Specializing in elderly care and medication administration.

Provided critical care nursing in the intensive care unit. Managed ventilators, administered medications, and monitored patients with complex medical conditions. Collaborated with medical teams for patient care planning.
Worked in the critical care unit providing specialized nursing care to critically ill patients. Managed complex medical equipment and provided family support during difficult times.
Currently working as a senior ICU nurse providing expert critical care services. Leading nursing teams and mentoring junior staff while maintaining high standards of patient care.
Started career as a staff nurse in the general medical ward. Developed foundational nursing skills and gained experience in patient assessment and care delivery.
Provided specialized nursing care to children and adolescents. Managed pediatric medications, family education, and emotional support for young patients and their families.
Worked in the pediatric ward providing care to children with various medical conditions. Developed expertise in child development and family-centered care approaches.
Currently working as a community pediatric nurse providing healthcare services to children in their homes and community settings. Supporting families with children with complex health needs.
Provided mental health nursing care in acute psychiatric units. Managed crisis interventions, medication administration, and therapeutic interventions for patients with mental health conditions.
Worked in community mental health services providing support to individuals with mental health conditions. Conducted assessments, care planning, and crisis management.
Currently working as a senior mental health nurse leading teams in acute psychiatric care. Providing expert mental health interventions and mentoring junior staff.
Started nursing career in general medical ward before specializing in mental health nursing. Developed foundational nursing skills and patient care experience.

Provided specialized care to elderly patients in geriatric wards. Managed complex care needs, medication administration, and family support for patients with dementia and other age-related conditions.
Specialized in dementia care providing support to patients with Alzheimer's and other forms of dementia. Developed expertise in behavioral management and family education.
Currently working as a community care nurse providing healthcare services to elderly patients in their homes. Supporting patients with complex care needs and palliative care requirements.
